  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "####  2. **Select a range**",
   "id": "342e981fd365ef1a"
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "# start : stop : start\n",
    "players=['Player_0','Player_9']"
   ],
   "id": "ef61767cdfe24da0",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df.loc[players,'age':'club']",
   "id": "4bedb6cc6ef33e42",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df.index",
   "id": "70a1dd04fe431b5",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df.loc['Player_0':'Player_9','age':'club']",
   "id": "9071715abe1299b3",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "#### 2.1  **Select with condition**",
   "id": "bd52b4e4adcf337c"
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df.loc[df['weight_kg']>80,'age':'club']",
   "id": "c88e7ae89bbff866",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "df.loc[(df['weight_kg']>80) & (df['height_cm']>181),'age':'club']\n",
    "# Multiple conditions"
   ],
   "id": "57e7c0bd3cab600",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "### **Above are loc , Now are iloc**\n",
    "### **loc()选的是columns的名字，iloc选的是columns的index，可以把他看做坐标系**"
   ],
   "id": "ddc7b524bb89282e"
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "df.set_index('short_name',inplace=True)\n",
    "df.iloc[23,8]\n",
    "df.iloc[:,6]"
   ],
   "id": "ca9e1b83d8e1ab4f",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df.head()",
   "id": "af7b8f734dedd27c",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "df.iloc[[1,7],2:6]\n",
    "#左闭右开。2取6不取。0为sofifa_id，6为weight_kg，只取到5"
   ],
   "id": "8a9055d520de74ed",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "# With condition\n",
    "list(df['weight_kg'>80])\n",
    "# 语义：从 df 中选出那些 体重 > 80 的行，且显示 1 到 7 列 , Multiple Condition同样可用\n",
    "df[df['weight_kg'] > 80].iloc[:, 1:7]"
   ],
   "id": "c617d682e733b54",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
