  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "### 6 **Sample() and Random**",
   "id": "cf95c79e7d2fdea9"
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df['dob'].sample(10,random_state=99)# 就是从哪里开始随机的意思",
