  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "#### 8. **Apply (),对row or column实现自定义函数的作用**",
   "id": "96199826cea1441b"
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df['age'].apply(np.sqrt).head()",
   "id": "d5a4be3f2ddfe6bf",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "def bmi(row):\n",
    "    return row['weight_kg']/(row['height_cm']/100)**2"
   ],
   "id": "f899096a7969064e",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "df.apply(bmi,axis=1)",
   "id": "cf4e227816f28ef",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "#### **Lambda +apply()**",
